        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ONSITE_1",
          "next": "N_SECV_ONSITE_2",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Vestibule doesn\u0019t count as onsite in the system.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ONSITE_2",
          "next": "N_SECV_ONSITE_3",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "It\u0019s a buffer room. (pause) You\u0019re contained in there. (pause) System still doesn\u0019t see you as \u0018here\u0019.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ONSITE_3",
          "next": "N_SECV_ONSITE_MENU",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Onsite is a timestamp (pause) and a name the log will take. (pause) If I can't tie the door to that, (pause) I can't open it.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "choices": [
            {
              "checks": [],
              "id": "ASK_WITH_ROOM",
              "next": "N_SECV_ROOM_1",
              "text": "(ask) So what do I do with what\u2019s in this room?"
            },
            {
              "checks": [],
              "id": "LEAVE_ENDCALL",
              "next": "N_SECV_ENDCALL_1",
              "text": "(leave) End call."
            }
          ],
          "id": "N_SECV_ONSITE_MENU",
          "speakerId": "PLAYER",
          "type": "player_choice"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ROOM_1",
          "next": "N_SECV_ROOM_2",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Use what\u0019s there. (pause) You need something Records accepts.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ROOM_2",
          "next": "N_SECV_ROOM_3",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "A Presence Receipt. (pause) A stamp. (pause) A kiosk printout. (pause) Anything I can point to in the log (pause) when I hit the door.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ROOM_3",
          "next": "N_END",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Give me paper. I can help. (pause) Without it I can\u2019t be the one.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_BADGES_1",
          "next": "N_SECV_BADGES_2",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Blank forms don\u2019t do much until marked.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_BADGES_2",
          "next": "N_SECV_BADGES_3",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "It won\u2019t authorize you. (pause) But it\u2019s something on paper. (pause) Later you can still say you signed in. (pause) Sort of.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_BADGES_3",
          "next": "N_SECV_BADGES_4",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "If you can get a Records marker (pause) onto one of those stamp or kiosk things (pause) then I can treat you as accountable (pause) and run doors.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_BADGES_4",
          "next": "N_END",
          "speakerId": "PLAYER",
          "text": "Understood.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_OLEA_1",
          "next": "N_SECV_OLEA_2",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "I can log that you called. (pause) I can\u0019t log you onsite from this box.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_OLEA_2",
          "next": "N_SECV_OLEA_3",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "That onsite flag has to come from Records. (pause) Or the kiosk workflow. (pause) It\u0019s database fields. (pause) I\u0019m not taking it on faith over audio.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_OLEA_3",
          "next": "N_SECV_OLEA_MENU",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "If I mark you present without it, (pause) the audit trail points straight at me. (pause) I\u0019m cleared to respond to a record\u0014(pause) not create one.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "choices": [
            {
              "checks": [],
              "id": "ASK_MIN",
              "next": "N_SECV_MIN_1",
              "text": "(ask) Fine. Minimum requirement?"
            },
            {
              "checks": [],
              "id": "LEAVE_ENDCALL",
              "next": "N_SECV_ENDCALL_1",
              "text": "(leave) End call."
            }
          ],
          "id": "N_SECV_OLEA_MENU",
          "speakerId": "PLAYER",
          "type": "player_choice"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_MIN_1",
          "next": "N_SECV_MIN_2",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Minimum? Name. Date. Type. (pause) Site\u2019s set to onsite. (pause) And a Records authority marker.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_MIN_2",
          "next": "N_END",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Stamp is cleanest. (pause) Kiosk receipt works. (pause) Handwritten note\u0014people love it. (pause) It falls apart the second anyone pushes.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
          "id": "N_SECV_ENDCALL_1",
          "next": "N_END",
          "speakerId": "SECV_OPERATOR",
          "text": "Okay. (pause) Call me back when you\u0019re marked onsite. (pause) I know you\u0019re boxed in right now. (pause) Watch yourself.",
          "type": "npc_line"
        },
        {
